directions:
Directions to Wake Forest University
From North/East: Take I-95 south to I-85 south to I-40 west. In Winston-Salem take Business I-40: Exit onto Cherry St. North (Exit 5).  Cherry St.  becomes University Parkway.  WFU entrance will be on your left.   
From North/West: Take I-77 south to I-74 / US 52 south. Take the University Parkway exit- (Exit 115).  WFU entrance will be on your right.
From South: Take I-77 north to I-40 east. In Winston-Salem take Business I-40: Exit onto Cherry St. North (Exit 5). Cherry St.  becomes University Parkway.  WFU entrance will be on your left.   
From West: Take I-40 east to Winston-Salem. From Business I-40: Exit onto Cherry St. North (Exit 5). Cherry St.  becomes University Parkway.  WFU entrance will be on your left.
